Government office services
As a user i can search the office hour
As a user i can search the office by name
                                    location
                                    services
                                    user-group
                                    phone #
As a user i can get how do get there
As a user i can get info what do i need to have to get the services
As a user i can get info how long it takes to finish all services
As a user i can get office address/ phone/email/website
As a user i can contact with someone to get more support/info with call/chat
As a user i can get notification from the office i agree to receive notification

As an admin i can update info on the app


Diary
As a user i can add entry anytime
As a user i can edit entry anytime
As a user i can update entry anytime
As a user i can delete entry anytime
As a user i can add day,date, year of every entry
As a user i can add descriptive header/title for every entry
As a user i can have profile
As a user i can add my feeling in it's own space for every entry
As a user i need to have a picture that can express the feeling based on the entry
As a user i need to have advice every morning based on the cumulative feeling or the most urgent dominant feeling
